
 1ï¸âƒ£ JavaScript Variables

Variables store data values.

 ğŸ”¹ Ways to Declare Variables

| Keyword | Scope      | Reassign | Hoisting | Use Case        |
| - | - | -- | -- |  |
| `var`   | Function   | âœ…        | Yes      | Old JS (avoid)  |
| `let`   | Block `{}` | âœ…        | No       | Changing values |
| `const` | Block `{}` | âŒ        | No       | Fixed values    |

js
